node.text:
Hit the #CreachTube for a Bonus round of INTRUDERS where @larbvomit lets us raid his trunk, and gives us a history lesson on the many iterations of some of his favorite creations that all started out with a jigsaw in the SHED. All of this and more in Episode 1 of INTRUDERS Now Playing at the 🔗 in BIO!
Filmed: @justsomedude @paconertz
Edit: @trevarcushing

#CreatureSkateboards #CreatureFiends

node.title: What is @larbvomit hiding in his trunk😈?!
